spec_data.Name: perl-Memoize-ExpireLRU
spec_data.Description:
This module implements an expiry policy for Memoize that follows LRU
semantics, that is, the last n results, where n is specified as the
argument to the CACHESIZE parameter, will be cached.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 01:16:46 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Expiry plug-in for Memoize that adds LRU cache expiration
